(42, 18, 16, 1, 21, 4, 4, 'suffer little children to come unto me', 'Children and Covenant Relationship', 'This connection highlights the importance of children in God''s plan. Both passages emphasize the inclusion of children in significant covenantal acts, with Jesus welcoming them and Abraham circumcising Isaac as commanded.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
